<li id="fn:2">
<p><a href="http://www.codeproject.com/Articles/247289/In-place-editing-with-ASP-NET-Repeater">codeproject: In-place Editing with ASP.NET Repeater</a><a href="#fnref:2" rev="footnote">&#8617;</a></p></li>
</ol>
